arStrings.szText: "What are the Burned Knights doing in Nahantu?"
Searching for Neyrelle, of course. They would wield her like a blade to deepen the schism in our faith. Only violence and misery would come from their success.
Few know what Neyrelle has in her possession. Captain Kharov is one of those people. Even mad, we would be fools to underestimate him.
